title: Official Initial Rankings for Midnights!
description:
Ok now that we have all had a moment to breathe and hopefully, sleep, it's time to make some official rankings. We were still shell-shocked and awaiting the chaotic announcement at the last rankings. Now we feel like we can give more well thought out answers!
And a BIG THANK YOU to all of our friends that joined us for our live stream and those that came out to our celebration party. WE HAD A BLAST AND ABSOLUTELY LOVE YOU ALL! Thank you for being there with us!
And next time... We will be breaking down Lavender Haze!
